msgid "A live <em>ledger</em> of coding interviews."
msgstr "程式面試的即時 <em>紀錄</em>。"

msgid ""
"Issue a single-use token URL to a candidate, observe the live editor in real "
"time, and review submissions, anti-cheat events, and snapshot replays after "
"the session ends."
msgstr ""
"發送一次性連結給候選人，即時觀看其作答畫面；面試結束後可檢視提交、防作弊事件"
"與作答回放。"

